This is the best-in-slot available equipment for maging the Kraken. The set up shown in this section currently costs approximately {{Coins|{{GEP|Black mask}} + {{GEP|Occult necklace}} + {{GEP|Nightmare staff}} + {{GEP|Harmonised orb}} + {{GEP|Ancestral robe top}} + {{GEP|Ancestral robe bottom}} + {{GEP|Tome of fire (empty)}} + {{GEP|Burnt page|100}} + {{GEP|Tormented bracelet}} + {{GEP|Eternal boots}} + {{GEP|Ring of suffering}} + {{GEP|Volatile orb}} + {{GEP|Nightmare staff}} + {{GEP|Imbued heart}}}} coins. See the table below for an overview of equipment alternatives in case this setup is not accessible or too expensive.

===Notes===
*Casting [[fire spells]] with a charged [[tome of fire]] equipped will increase the spell's damage by 50%.
*The [[occult necklace]] (+10%), [[tormented bracelet]] (+5%), [[imbued god capes]] (+2%) and [[ancestral robes]] (+2% each) increase the maximum hit of the player's Magic spells.
*[[Rune pouch]] to hold rune drops.
*The [[Imbued heart]] will increase your damage and reduce the damage you take considerably. 
*1-2 [[Prayer potion]]s or [[Super restore]]s for using the [[Preserve]] prayer to keep imbued heart stats up.
*[[Dramen staff]] for fairy ring {{Fairycode|akq}}, if elite Lumbridge diary is not completed.
* Instead of a Dramen staff, a [[Piscatoris teleport]] puts you near the kraken cave whilst saving an inventory slot. However [[Home Teleport]] will need to be used to leave.
*[[Explorer's ring 4]] for high alchemy if not bringing runes.
*[[Eldritch nightmare staff]]'s special attack will restore your prayer, allowing you to keep [[Augury]] and [[Preserve]] on for the imbued heart boost to maintain high magic defence.
*The [[Toxic blowpipe]] offers a much cheaper option for those who do not want to spend money on the Eldritch/Volatile nightmare staffs. One may consider using its special attack on the [[Enormous Tentacle]]s, as they have a slightly lower +270 ranged defence bonus compared to the Kraken's +300. However, although the Kraken takes heavily reduced ranged damage, the blowpipe special attack will still grant the full health replenishment. Despite having a +270 (or +300 for Kraken) ranged defence bonus, you will still hit often because the Kraken and its tentacles have a level one base defence level. This is especially useful when wearing Karils or Armadyl armour.
*The [[Volatile nightmare staff]] is a good special attack option if you're looking to farm Kraken as fast as possible.
*The [[Elysian spirit shield]] does not work against the [[Kraken]]'s attacks, as they're typeless and are able to hit through prayer. However, the passive effect greatly reduces damage taken from Kraken’s tentacles.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/jagexash/status/635867849970442240|date=24 August 2015|archiveurl=https://archive.ph/lRDSu|archivedate=9 April 2022|quote=It does not work on attacks that hit through prayers like that kraken boss attack.|name=ely}}

